    "description_long": "This is a triangular traffic warning sign mounted on a tall, cylindrical metal post. The sign face is white with a bold black exclamation mark centered inside, bordered by a thick red outline, indicating a general caution or warning. The post appears metallic and sturdy, with a slightly textured finish and capped ends. The rear of the sign is plain and unmarked, showing the metallic backing of the triangular plate. The overall construction suggests durability for outdoor urban environments, with materials designed to withstand weather exposure. The sign is typically used to alert drivers and pedestrians to potential hazards or changes in road conditions ahead.",
